97 void LLVMAddInternalizePass(LLVMPassManagerRef PM, unsigned AllButMain) {
98  std::vector<const char *> Export;
99  if (AllButMain)
100  Export.push_back("main");
101  unwrap(PM)->add(createInternalizePass(Export));
102 }
